&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">lsblk &lt;span class="c1"># 显示分区信息&lt;/span>
