&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pacman -S grub efibootmgr &lt;span class="c1"># grub是启动引导器，efibootmgr被 grub 脚本用来将启动项写入 NVRAM。&lt;/span>
